&lt;h3&gt;Custom ParameterResolver&lt;/h3&gt;

In case you want to define an own argument source, for example from a non-CSV file, you have to implement own `ParameterResolver` and instroduce a custom annotation:

```java
@Target(ElementType.FIELD)
@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
@Documented
@ExtendWith(FileResourceParameterResolver.class)
@interface FileResource {

